A '''Hyper adrenaline amplifier''' was an advanced model of the [[adrenaline amplifier]] belt that monitored adrenaline in the wearer's bloodstream. When the levels elevated in combat, a large additional dose of adrenaline was released. This greatly enhanced reaction time.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''

